{"tid":2164851,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"女學生急救途中被救護車直送殯儀館","createTime":"2020-08-19T12:16:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-19T12:42:34.000Z","uid":312115,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e75254edde6070c1ff8164555f5a957e76c3112f","tid":2164851,"uid":312115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T12:16:55.000Z","msg":"［有線中國組］六月中江蘇鹽城一個中三女學生，在課室突然暈倒，校方隨即送她到衛生院，同時叫救護車。<br />\n<br />\n女生母親說，急救員趕到衛生院時，指該女生已沒有生命跡象，但在衛生院勸喻下，答應送女生到縣人民醫院搶救，但救護車直接開到殯儀館，跟車的老師投訴，而且殯儀館基於沒有醫院死亡證拒收後，再把女生送到醫院搶救，最終女生死亡。<br />\n<br />\n官方回應指是安撫家屬，才把女生抬上救護車，做法合規。<br />\n<br />\n#送院變送殯儀館<br />\n#有線中國組<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c777c5c02d2ac6ed15fa467a5287b1241b5ce2c","tid":2164851,"uid":155095,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T12:24:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media.whatscap.com/4d8/236/4d8236a09c1dde2e980680b75ea0b049bc12256a_n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.whatscap.com%2F4d8%2F236%2F4d8236a09c1dde2e980680b75ea0b049bc12256a_n.jpg&h=c9b3d386&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b3b09132e975cffd9019f0e266bb0fc58834ba8b","tid":2164851,"uid":50740,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T12:27:07.000Z","msg":"最後咪合情合法合理<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef3c0d29fc3b464ca5a69329d03767cdb435d116","tid":2164851,"uid":38572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T12:28:22.000Z","msg":"支那野係咁上下"},{"pid":"ccf6a52b23844f05de373d081c7704c463ae1f85","tid":2164851,"ui